data.description: Check out this cozy home on a 1/2 acre lot! Plenty of parking space right beside the one-car garage and extra-long parking slab. Mature vegetation adorns your new front yard! Inside this carpet-free home, you will find a perfect white canvas ready for you to let your inner decorator shine! Good size bedrooms and handsome vanity base cabinets in both bathrooms! Huge laundry room - Space for a folding table or a pantry! Ready for you, there are two storage sheds with double doors for convenient access. 1/2 acre to keep all your toys! See this charming home today!
